<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 26, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Ventura County Life; Part J; Page 12 
</P>
