perform at The Pond of Anaheim. * Aug. 10: Meat Loaf, grandiose rock singer, 
plays at Irvine Meadows. * Aug. 24: Earthy country singer Jerry Jeff Walker 
appears at the Coach House. TOPS IN MUSIC/DANCE * May 28 and 29: The Brockus 
