maintenance 479,035 167,728 Office 887,866 465,910 Equipment 161,370 5,500 
Sources: Orange County Grand Jury, Orange County Public Library 
</P>
<P>
 * CHECKING OUT 
</P>
<P>
 Mission Viejo completes plans to leave county system and build a $6-million 
library. B4 
</P>
