 Three cities on the Palos Verdes Peninsula are seeking volunteers to work with 
the Lomita sheriff's station. 
</P>
<P>
 Volunteers from Rancho Palos Verdes, Rolling Hills and Rolling Hills Estates 
will be trained to help the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department, 
particularly during times of civil unrest or natural disaster. 
</P>
<P>
